<body>
<div class="guideline-container">
    
    <h1>RoomRander Community Guidelines</h1>
    <p class="highlight">Last Updated: November 20, 2025</p>
    <p>
        Welcome to RoomRander! To maintain a safe, respectful, and trustworthy
        environment for all users—tenants, hosts, and visitors—we have established the
        following Community Guidelines. By using our platform, you agree to follow
        these rules to ensure a positive experience for everyone.
    </p>

    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Respect & Safety</h2>
        <p>Your behavior shapes our community. Treat others kindly and respectfully.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>No abusive, threatening, or hateful language.</li>
            <li>No harassment, discrimination, or bullying of any form.</li>
            <li>Respect personal boundaries and privacy of others.</li>
            <li>Report unsafe behavior immediately using our support tools.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. Accurate & Honest Listings</h2>
        <p>Hosts must provide information that is truthful and up-to-date.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>All room details, prices, and amenities must be accurate.</li>
            <li>Upload real images—no misleading or stolen photos.</li>
            <li>Keep listings updated if price or availability changes.</li>
            <li>No false claims about location, facilities, or services.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Genuine Bookings</h2>
        <p>Use the platform responsibly and only for real accommodation needs.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>No fake or duplicate accounts.</li>
            <li>No spam bookings or fraudulent demands.</li>
            <li>Follow all platform processes for cancellations or disputes.</li>
            <li>Payment gateway and booking system will be introduced soon—misuse will not be tolerated.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 4 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Cleanliness & Property Care</h2>
        <p>Tenants and hosts share responsibility for maintaining a healthy living environment.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Keep the property clean and damage-free.</li>
            <li>Follow host guidelines regarding usage of space.</li>
            <li>Report property issues promptly.</li>
            <li>Respect shared spaces and other occupants.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 5 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. No Illegal Activities</h2>
        <p>Illegal behavior is strictly prohibited and may lead to removal and legal action.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>No unlawful gatherings, substances, or actions.</li>
            <li>No fraudulent documents or identity misrepresentation.</li>
            <li>No unauthorized subletting or commercial activity.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 6 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>6. Communication & Support</h2>
        <p>All users must communicate politely and responsibly.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Use phone, email, or in-app messaging respectfully.</li>
            <li>No spamming or sending irrelevant content.</li>
            <li>Contact support for disputes, safety issues, or reporting violations.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 7 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>7. Data Privacy</h2>
        <p>Your personal data is safe with us and must not be misused by any user.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>No sharing private information without consent.</li>
            <li>Do not attempt to access someone else’s data.</li>
            <li>RoomRander follows strict privacy and data protection policies.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 8 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>8. Future Enhancements</h2>
        <p>We are continuously evolving to offer a more secure, smart, and user-friendly experience.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>AI-Based Room Prediction System (Coming Soon)</li>
            <li>Smart Room Recommendation Engine</li>
            <li>Online Payment Gateway (UPI, Cards, Wallets)</li>
            <li>Complete Room Booking System</li>
            <li>User Dashboard (Profile, Saved Listings, Messages)</li>
            <li>Owner Dashboard (Listings, Earnings, Analytics)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 9 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>9. Violations & Consequences</h2>
        <p>If guidelines are violated, the following actions may be taken:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Warning notice or temporary suspension</li>
            <li>Permanent account deletion for severe cases</li>
            <li>Listing removal</li>
            <li>Legal action (where required)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Your safety and trust matter. We act quickly against bad behavior.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 10 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>10. Staying Updated</h2>
        <p>
            These guidelines may be updated over time. Users will be notified of any
            important changes, and updated versions will always be available on our website.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">© 2025 RoomRander Ltd. All Rights Reserved.</div>

</div>
